name: Rules
text:
The corporation may adopt all rules necessary to carry out the purpose of this subpart, including rules relating to determining preference among applicants for state rent supplements. [L 1997, c 350, pt of §2]
    [Section effective July 1, 2006.  For section effective until June 30, 2006, see above.]  The administration may adopt all rules necessary to carry out the purpose of this subpart, including rules relating to determining preference among applicants for state rent supplements. [L 1997, c 350, pt of §2; am L 2005, c 196, §26(a)]
